&lt;h1 id=&#34;应用&#34;&gt;应用&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;rc电路-lpf&#34;&gt;RC电路-LPF&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;图示&#34;&gt;图示&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8/2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;408&#34;
	height=&#34;418&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8/2_hubed56d1da9f14bfe76df5fca69b58125_26084_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8/2_hubed56d1da9f14bfe76df5fca69b58125_26084_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;97&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;234px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;推导&#34;&gt;推导&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
H(\omega) = \frac{\frac{1}{j\omega C}}{\frac{1}{j\omega C}+R} = \frac{\frac{1}{RC}}{j\omega + \frac{1}{RC}} = \frac{\frac{1}{RC}}{\sqrt{\omega^2 + (\frac{1}{RC}})^2}e^{-jtan^{-1}(\omega RC)} \\\
\\ \therefore |H(\omega)| = \frac{\frac{1}{RC}}{\sqrt{\omega^2 + (\frac{1}{RC}})^2} \\\
\\ \angle H(\omega) = tan^{-1}(\omega RC) \\\
\\ 当\omega = \frac{1}{RC}时，|H(\omega)| = \frac{1}{\sqrt 2} ，Gain = 20lg(|H(\omega)|) = -3.01(dB) \\\
\\ 其中，\omega_0 = \frac{1}{RC}叫做3dB的截止频率
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;结论&#34;&gt;结论&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RC电路是LPF（低通滤波器）&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;cr电路-hpf&#34;&gt;CR电路-HPF&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;图示-1&#34;&gt;图示&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8/3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;331&#34;
	height=&#34;365&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8/3_huafb27d41edc7ace42f77caaaee97f63f_15297_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8/3_huafb27d41edc7ace42f77caaaee97f63f_15297_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;90&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;217px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;推导-1&#34;&gt;推导&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
同理，H(\omega) = \frac{\omega}{\sqrt{\omega^2 + (\frac{1}{RC})^2}} e^{j\Big[\frac{\pi}{2} - tan^{-1}(\omega RC) \Big]} \\\
\\ |H(\omega)| = \frac{\omega}{\sqrt{\omega^2 + (\frac{1}{RC})^2}}  \\\
\\ \angle H(\omega) =\frac{\pi}{2} - tan^{-1}(\omega RC) \\\
\\ 当\omega_0 = \frac{1}{RC}时，可以得出与RC电路相同的计算结果
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;串联rlc-lpf&#34;&gt;串联RLC-LPF&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;图示-2&#34;&gt;图示&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8/4.png&#34;
	width=&#34;546&#34;
	height=&#34;374&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8/4_hua00edcca8f4b32c48c468c1d297dfd04_33686_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8/4_hua00edcca8f4b32c48c468c1d297dfd04_33686_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
