&lt;h3 id=&#34;推导-2&#34;&gt;推导&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
H(\omega) = \frac{\frac{1}{LC}}{-\omega^2 + \frac{R}{L}j\omega + \frac{1}{LC}} \\\
\\ |H(\omega)| = \frac{\omega^2}{\sqrt{\Big(\frac{1}{LC} - \omega^2\Big)^2 } + \Big( \frac{R}{L}\omega\Big)^2} \\\
\\ \angle H(\omega) = \pi - tan^{-1}\Big(\frac{\frac{R}L{\omega}}{\frac{1}{LC}- \omega^2} \Big) \\\
\\ 转角频率 \omega_0 = \frac{1}{\sqrt{LC}}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;串联rcl-hpf&#34;&gt;串联RCL-HPF&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;电路&#34;&gt;电路&lt;/h3&gt;
