&lt;h3 id=&#34;推导-3&#34;&gt;推导&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
H(\omega) = \frac{\frac{R}{L}j\omega}{-\omega^2 + \frac{R}{L}j\omega + \frac{1}{LC}} \\\
\\ |H(\omega)| = \frac{\frac{R}{L}\omega}{\sqrt{\Big(\frac{1}{LC} - \omega^2\Big)^2  + \Big( \frac{R}{L}\omega\Big)^2}} \\\
\\ \angle H(\omega) = \frac{\pi}{2} - tan^{-1}\Big(\frac{\frac{R}L{\omega}}{\frac{1}{LC}- \omega^2} \Big) \\\
\\ 转角频率 \omega_0 = \frac{1}{\sqrt{LC}} \\\
\\ 下截止频率 \ \omega_1 = -\frac{R}{2L} + \frac{R}{2L} \sqrt{1 + \frac{4L}{R^2C}} \\\
\\ 上截止频率 \ \omega_2 = \frac{R}{2L} + \frac{R}{2L} \sqrt{1 + \frac{4L}{R^2C}} \\\
\\ 3dB带宽 \omega_{3dB} =\omega_2 - \omega_1 =\frac{R}{L}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;串联rcl-bsf&#34;&gt;串联RCL-BSF&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;电路-1&#34;&gt;电路&lt;/h3&gt;
