|H(\omega)| = \frac{|V_o|}{|V_{in}|} = |\frac{sL+\frac{1}{sC}}{sL + \frac{1}{sC}+R}| \overset{除以L,乘以s}{=}  \\\
\\ \Big|\frac{\frac{1}{LC}-\omega^2}{\frac{1}{LC}-\omega^2 + j\frac{\omega R}{L}}\Big| =  \\\
\\ \frac{\frac{1}{LC}-\omega^2}{\sqrt{(\frac{1}{LC}-\omega^2)^2 + (\frac{\omega R}{L})^2 }} \\\
\\ \angle H(\omega) = tan^{-1}\Big( \frac{\frac{\omega R}{L}}{\frac{1}{LC}-\omega^2} \Big)
$$&lt;/p&gt;
